## 1. Project Overview

**hmpsn.studio** is an SEO/web analytics platform built with **React 18 + Vite + TailwindCSS** (frontend) and **Express + TypeScript** (backend). It manages client websites via Webflow, Google Search Console, GA4, and SEMRush integrations.

- **No database** — all data is JSON on disk via `~/.asset-dashboard/` and per-workspace folders
- **AI** — OpenAI GPT-4.1/4.1-mini/4.1-nano via `server/openai-helpers.ts` (`callOpenAI` with retry, timeout, token tracking)
- **Payments** — Stripe Checkout (not Payment Intents). Config encrypted on disk (AES-256-GCM). Admin UI for keys + products.
- **Auth** — Dual system: internal JWT (7-day, admin) + client JWT (24h, per-workspace). Legacy shared-password still supported.
- **Monetization** — 3 tiers (Free/Growth/Premium), per-item content purchases, 14-day Growth trial, UX soft-gating via `<TierGate>`

